   ```

## Instructions

### 1. Create or Enter Worktree

Follow `/rules/worktree-operations.md`:

```bash
# If worktree doesn't exist, create it
if ! git worktree list | grep -q "epic-$ARGUMENTS"; then
  git checkout main
